44
00:01:32,280 --> 00:01:34,400
Don't be so dramatic, Chief.

45
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:35,640
What happened on earth?

46
00:01:36,480 --> 00:01:38,440
You got sued by the Fu family

47
00:01:38,480 --> 00:01:40,320
for the comic you made.

48
00:01:41,160 --> 00:01:42,880
They sued us for infringement. Look.

49
00:01:44,215 --> 00:01:45,115
(Lawyer's letter)

50
00:01:45,240 --> 00:01:47,560
We got sued by such powerful people.

51
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:49,400
My dream of publishing national comics

52
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:50,920
was nipped in the bud.

53
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:00,520
Chief.

54
00:02:01,240 --> 00:02:02,440
How about this?

55
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,360
How about

56
00:02:05,240 --> 00:02:07,360
