for the last two months first?

57
00:02:10,640 --> 00:02:12,040
Are you nuts?

58
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:12,400
I...

59
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:14,200
You brought such trouble to my company.

60
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:15,240
And now you are asking for money?

61
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:18,280
