67
00:02:28,640 --> 00:02:30,760
Well, I...

68
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:35,480
Oh, my sweetie.

69
00:02:35,480 --> 00:02:37,040
Here. Have some milk, my baby.

70
00:02:37,080 --> 00:02:39,720
