77
00:02:54,160 --> 00:02:55,600
He has none.

78
00:02:56,160 --> 00:02:57,320
You have a dad to love you too, right?

79
00:02:58,080 --> 00:02:59,520
He's going to have none.

80
00:03:00,320 --> 00:03:02,520
You never had an empty stomach, right?

81
00:03:03,720 --> 00:03:05,240
This is his last bottle of milk.

82
00:03:07,920 --> 00:03:09,320
Please help us.

83
00:03:09,600 --> 00:03:10,120
Get up, Chief.

84
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:11,600
Don't do this to me. Get up.

85
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:12,920
I beg you.

86
00:03:12,920 --> 00:03:13,880
Chief.

87
